00:06:19.520 --> 00:06:22.870
that might make you as
a parent or an educator

00:06:22.870 --> 00:06:27.150
or a librarian feel a little big
uncomfortable, that's why books

00:06:27.150 --> 00:06:29.830
like these actually matter to
kids because they want to talk

00:06:29.830 --> 00:06:33.280
about that stuff that is
making them feel alone

00:06:33.280 --> 00:06:36.720
and uncomfortable and marginalized.

00:06:36.720 --> 00:06:45.560
