00:41:39.460 --> 00:41:41.530
and I know like you're
waiting for David Baldacci

00:41:41.530 --> 00:41:43.050
and he's probably here [laughter].

00:41:43.050 --> 00:41:49.810
It's like "Get her off," but
so last night, they, you know,

00:41:49.810 --> 00:41:52.420
they gave this really great
award to Dennis Johnson,

00:41:52.420 --> 00:41:55.750
who is a great fiction writer
who passed away, right,

00:41:55.750 --> 00:41:59.830
and I was telling my agent that he
visited this program that I used

00:41:59.830 --> 00:42:01.520
to work for at the
University of Minnesota,

00:42:01.520 --> 00:42:05.390
and one of the graduate students
