or if he just, you know.

00:42:17.830 --> 00:42:19.130
I like to think it's true.

00:42:19.130 --> 00:42:22.110
He was a really funny
person in person.

00:42:22.110 --> 00:42:24.340
I really liked meeting him.

00:42:24.340 --> 00:42:28.940
He said, "[Sigh] You
know, I watch a lot of TV.

00:42:28.940 --> 00:42:34.260
I just-I got this cabin that
I-you know, I watch a lot of TV,

00:42:34.260 --> 00:42:40.480
and then my wife comes over to me,
and she says, 'We need a new roof,

00:42:40.480 --> 00:42:45.100
and I get up and turn off the TV,
and I go write, and I sell a book,

00:42:45.100 --> 00:42:48.260
