got to pay the electric bill,

00:42:57.580 --> 00:42:59.480
and I get up, and
I turn off the TV,

00:42:59.480 --> 00:43:01.690
and then I go write
something, and I sell it."

00:43:01.690 --> 00:43:03.220
And you know what?

00:43:03.220 --> 00:43:04.640
That's inspiration.

00:43:04.640 --> 00:43:09.250
Sometimes you just get up and
turn off the TV and put your butt

00:43:09.250 --> 00:43:11.880
